;;    ██╔════╝╚██╗ ██╔╝██╔══██╗╚════██╗██╔══██╗╚══██╔══╝██║  ██║███║██╔════╝██║   ██║██╔════╝╚══███╔╝     
;;    ██║      ╚████╔╝ ██████╔╝ █████╔╝██████╔╝   ██║   ███████║╚██║█████╗  ██║   ██║█████╗    ███╔╝      
;;    ██║       ╚██╔╝  ██╔══██╗ ╚═══██╗██╔══██╗   ██║   ██╔══██║ ██║██╔══╝  ╚██╗ ██╔╝██╔══╝   ███╔╝       
;;    ╚██████╗   ██║   ██████╔╝██████╔╝██║  ██║   ██║   ██║  ██║ ██║███████╗ ╚████╔╝ ███████╗███████╗     
;;     ╚═════╝   ╚═╝   ╚═════╝ ╚═════╝ ╚═╝  ╚═╝   ╚═╝   ╚═╝  ╚═╝ ╚═╝╚══════╝  ╚═══╝  ╚══════╝╚══════╝     
;;																										 
;;																										 
;;																										 
;;    Copyright (C) Mahmoud Mohamed (00xWolf)  <https://github.com/mmsaeed509>								 
;;    LICENSE © GNU-GPL3
;;
;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;

at_pointer           = 1
stay_alive           = 1
csv_cmd              = pmenu
csv_no_dirs          = 0
tint2_look           = 0
terminal_exec        = bspterm -float &
terminal_args        = 
menu_width           = 200
menu_padding_top     = 5
menu_padding_right   = 5
menu_padding_bottom  = 5
menu_padding_left    = 5
menu_radius          = 15
menu_border          = 2
menu_halign          = left
sub_hover_action     = 1
item_margin_y        = 3
item_height          = 38
item_padding_x       = 10
item_radius          = 7
item_border          = 0
sep_height           = 5
font                 = JetBrainsMono Nerd Font 12px
icon_size            = 15
icon_theme           = ${ICONS}
arrow_string         = 

;; colors ;;
color_menu_bg        = ${BACKGROUND} 100
color_menu_border    = ${BLUE}
color_norm_bg        = ${BACKGROUND} 0
color_norm_fg        = ${FOREGROUND} 100
color_sel_bg         = ${FOREGROUND} 50
color_sel_fg         = ${FOREGROUND} 100
color_sep_fg         = ${FOREGROUND} 40       


	EOF
}

## Execute functions and run main 
main () {
	getcolors
	bspbar
	bspterm
	bsprofi
	bspdunst
	bspjgmenu
}

main
